<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/general.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/home.css">
        <title>Malaysian Club of Chicago - Home</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        {{>navbar}}
        <div id="right">
            <div id="group">
                <div id="overlay">
                    <h1>Malaysian Club of Chicago</h1>
                    <h2>Taste of Malaysia: Celebrating MCC 20th Anniversary & Malaysia Day</h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="half-point">
                <div style="max-width: 65%" class="text">
                    <h3>Jom makan!</h3>
                    <p>Taste of Malaysia 2019 will feature multiple booths to showcase a variety of Malaysian cuisine. Attendees will purchase tickets to buy different dishes. We will have Nasi Lemak, Char Koay Teow, Asam Laksa, Roti Canai, Chicken Curry, Satay, Mee Hoon, Kuih Lapis, Kuih Jagong, Bubur Kacang, Chendol, Durian (if in season) and more!</p>
                    <p class="annotate">Food items are always subject to change.</p>
                </div>
                <div id="image-part"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="static">
                <div class="vert-block">
                    <img src="./img/ex-1.jpg">
                    <div class="text">
                        <h3>Jom makan!</h3>
