                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="spacer"></div>
            <div class="hor-block left-img">
                <img src="./img/ex-2.jpg">
                <div class="wide-text text">
                    <p><strong>Date:</strong><br>September 14, 2019 (Saturday)</p>
                    <p><strong>Time:</strong><br>12pm - 3pm</p>
                    <p><strong>Location:</strong><br>Ned Brown Preserve (Busse Woods), Grove #26, Elk Grove Village IL 60007</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin: 50px auto; min-height: 410px;" class="hor-block right-img">
                <img src="./img/ex-3.png">
                <div class="wide-text text">
                    <p><strong>Early-Bird Ticket:</strong><br>$15 for 20 tickets</p>
                    <p><strong>Walk-In Ticket:</strong><br>$20 for 20 tickets</p>
